metadata.name: Human After All
metadata.description:
It's the story of a man who has lost all connection to his body and soul. Who got lost in all the noise, the gears of modern society. 
With his central nervous system in his hand, he rediscovers his reality.
He is a universe and speck of dust, alive and dead at the same time, he transcends time and space. 
He has found meaning in the void, existing.
